106
00:06:59,009 --> 00:07:00,308
Pegawai Takagi!

107
00:07:00,309 --> 00:07:01,309
Ya, tuan!

108
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:04,008
Maafkan saya, bolehkah kamu ambil cawan ini?

109
00:07:04,009 --> 00:07:05,909
Saya lebih rela...

110
