00:10:45,356 --> 00:10:47,155
Oh, begitu.

148
00:10:47,156 --> 00:10:49,056
Saya juga rasa begitu.

149
00:10:50,556 --> 00:10:52,055
"Wataru Tarumi (33)" -Semua jurukamera lain.

150
00:10:52,056 --> 00:10:54,455
"Jurukamera" -menggunakan kamera digital,

151
00:10:54,456 --> 00:10:58,755
